{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"62e06529a7","title":"四方面军有充分把握控制降静会定大道","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"b0ad2c479d","index":0,"year":1936,"month":9,"day":26,"articleId":"62e06529a7"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji9-1","name":"毛泽东全集第9卷(1)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji9-1.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji9-1":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"33ced1bb7f","type":"paragraph","text":"四方面军有充分把握控制","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"62e06529a7"},{"id":"63a5024cc6","type":"paragraph","text":"降静会定大道","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"62e06529a7"},{"id":"44ce4ffb6b","type":"paragraph","text":"1936年9月26日）朱、张：","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"62e06529a7"},{"id":"f7d2a7c432","type":"paragraph","text":"确息：胡宗南部到咸阳未动，其后续尚未到齐。四方面军有充分把握控制隆静会定大道，不会有严重战斗。一方面军可以主力南下策应，二方面军亦可向北移动钳制之。北上后粮食不成问题，若西进到甘西，则将被限制于青海一角，尔后行动困难","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"62e06529a7"},{"id":"a435b52703","type":"paragraph","text":"英洛恩博橡泽","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"62e06529a7"},{"id":"8d269e4222","type":"paragraph","text":"二十六日十二时","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"62e06529a7"},{"id":"af537b8d6e","type":"paragraph","text":"[1]这是毛泽东和林育英（张浩）、洛甫（张闻天）、周恩来、博古（秦邦宪）、王豫祥给朱德和红军总政治委员张国素的电报。","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"62e06529a7"},{"id":"1b64761011","type":"paragraph","text":"121胡宗南，当时任国民党军西北“”总司令部第一军军长兼第一师师长。","index":7,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"62e06529a7"},{"id":"b911503569","type":"paragraph","text":"[3]隆静会定大道，指甘肃隆德（今属宁夏）、静宁、会宁、定西间的公路。","index":8,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"62e06529a7"}],"page